Echo expression

Echo the results of any expression (after environment variable replacement) to stdout.

expression   -- Write this to stdout. Not quotes are required. Just like the Linux echo. 


Examples:
  ECHO Java is installed in ${java.home}
  Java is installed in C:\Program Files\Java\jre6
  
  ECHO I am $USERNAME
  I am greg
  
  ECHO The last query returned $ROW_COUNT rows
  The last query returned 23 rows
  
 